Spirit Pub Chief Executive Ian Dyson Plans to Quit, Times Says

-- B y   C a t h e r i n e   A i r l i e
-- 
2011-09-25T12:21:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/spirit-pub-chief-executive-ian-dyson-plans-to-quit-times-says.html
Spirit Pub Co. Chief Executive
Officer Ian Dyson plans to step down after a year at the U.K.
bar and restaurant chain, the Sunday Times reported, without
saying where it got the information.  Spirit separated from  Punch Taverns Plc (PUB)  last month, the
newspaper said. Scott Frankham, a spokesman for Spirit declined
to comment when contacted by Bloomberg News today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Catherine Airlie in  London  at 
 cairlie@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss at 
 sev@bloomberg.net  